 	  device.
 
+config STR_SMP
+	bool "Suspend to RAM SMP support (EXPERIMENTAL)"
+	depends on EXPERIMENTAL && ACPI_SLEEP && !X86_64
+	depends on HOTPLUG_CPU
+	default y
+	---help---
+	 enable Suspend to RAM SMP support. Some HT systems require this.
